22#ifndef netdissect_pcap_missing_h
23#define netdissect_pcap_missing_h
24
25/*
26 * Declarations of functions that might be missing from libpcap.
27 */
28
29#ifndef HAVE_PCAP_LIST_DATALINKS
30extern int pcap_list_datalinks(pcap_t *, int **);
31#endif
32
33#ifndef HAVE_PCAP_DATALINK_NAME_TO_VAL
34/*
35 * We assume no platform has one but not the other.
36 */
37extern int pcap_datalink_name_to_val(const char *);
38extern const char *pcap_datalink_val_to_name(int);
39#endif
40
41#ifndef HAVE_PCAP_DATALINK_VAL_TO_DESCRIPTION
42extern const char *pcap_datalink_val_to_description(int);
43#endif
44
45#ifndef HAVE_PCAP_DUMP_FTELL
46extern long pcap_dump_ftell(pcap_dumper_t *);
47#endif
48
49#endif /* netdissect_pcap_missing_h */
